//-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
//
// Reworked and adapted to MiSTer by Sorgelig@MiSTer (07.09.2018)
//
// Commodore 1541 gcr floppy (read/write) by Dar (darfpga@aol.fr) 23-May-2017
